Mod1 F1                     :RootMenu

Mod1 F2                     :ExecCommand urxvt
Mod1 Control T              :ExecCommand urxvt

Mod1 F4                     :Close
Mod4 Delete                 :KillWindow

Mod1 F10                    :MaximizeWindow
Mod4 Prior                  :MaximizeWindow
Mod4 Next                   :MinimizeWindow
Mod1 Tab                    :NextWindow (workspace=[current])

Mod1 F11                    :Fullscreen

Mod1 Control Left           :PrevWorkspace
Mod1 Control Right          :NextWorkspace
OnDesktop Mouse5            :NextWorkspace
OnDesktop Mouse4            :PrevWorkspace
OnToolbar Mouse5            :NextWorkspace
OnToolbar Mouse4            :PrevWorkspace
Mod4 Mouse5                 :NextWorkspace
Mod4 Mouse4                 :PrevWorkspace

Mod4 grave                  :Workspace 1
Mod4 1                      :Workspace 2
Mod4 2                      :Workspace 3
Mod4 3                      :Workspace 4
Mod4 4                      :Workspace 5
Mod4 5                      :Workspace 6
Mod4 6                      :Workspace 7

Mod1 Control Shift Left     :TakeToPrevWorkspace
Mod1 Control Shift Right    :TakeToNextWorkspace

Mod4 Left                   :MoveLeft   20
Mod4 Right                  :MoveRight  20
Mod4 Up                     :MoveUp     20
Mod4 Down                   :MoveDown   20
OnWindow Mod1 Mouse1        :MacroCmd {Raise} {Focus} {StartMoving}
OnWindowBorder Move1        :StartMoving
OnTitlebar Move1            :StartMoving

Shift Mod4 Left             :Resize     -1 0
Shift Mod4 Right            :Resize     +1 0
Shift Mod4 Up               :Resize     0 -1
Shift Mod4 Down             :Resize     0 +1
OnWindow Mod1 Mouse3        :MacroCmd {Raise} {Focus} {StartResizing BottomRight}

Mod4 C                      :MoveTo     0 0 Center
Mod4 KP_5                   :MoveTo     0 0 Center

OnDesktop Mouse1            :HideMenus
OnDesktop Mouse3            :RootMenu

Mod4 O                      :ExecCommand xclip -o | xargs xdg-open

